{"tid":1633600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚八點做咩好？","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:08:43.000Z","uid":35953,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6471a5fec50892584d87eecefddb4cef47fe2d29","tid":1633600,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚八點，全部人同我出嚟做你想做嘅野</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 --&gt; 商場唱歌/派傳單/痴文宣<br />\n勇武 --&gt; 拆鐵又好咩都好<br />\n<br />\n休咩息呀？！和理非就係要幫勇武cover!! 和理非print 定一大堆文宣幫手貼門口囉 (下面送埋幾張文宣比你做伸手黨呀）<br />\n<br />\n只要文宣做得好就ok, 71入立會就係一個好好嘅證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更何況拆鐵呢啲都唔係咩新野，依家先嚟吹風話停？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同嘅幫推<br />\n唔認同嘅留言討論<br />\n<br />\n註：mon post 狗死全家<br />\n<br />\n集合地點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1JR2pr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1JR2pr.jpg&h=8d251e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv1Twkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv1Twkz.jpg&h=0a4bde8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2vtkdV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2vtkdV.jpg&h=54c3445d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cq3q6TV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCq3q6TV.jpg&h=8a05b270&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea2a82de427c97459c5986762fe66555d289a381","tid":1633600,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"商場唱歌嘅就去返屋企附近商場<br />\n之前有唱過嗰啲"},{"pid":"e1bc58458c5e6c433c8be91868c75bc5f74239b2","tid":1633600,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:35:52.000Z","msg":"唔可以比佢停啊"},{